19
20 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
21
22 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code § 14-270-102(7), concerning the definition of
23 "property in kind" in relation to rural community projects, is amended to
24 read as follows:
25 (7) “Property in kind” means real or personal property "In-kind
26 donations" means committed goods and services, including without limitation:
27 (A) Real or personal property;
28 (B) Labor;
29 (C) Equipment;
30 (D) Materials;
31 (E) Services; and
32 (F) Money.
33
34 SECTION 2. Arkansas Code § 14-270-103(a)(2)(A), concerning when the
35 grant of state funds is authorized for rural community projects, is amended
36 to read as follows:
